---
title: Bacon & Tomato Pasta Salad with Parmesan & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Looking for a quick and easy lunch option? Whip up this pasta salad in just 15 minutes. Featuring crispy bacon, tomato and baby spinach tossed together in dangerously creamy dill and parsley mayo.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/642b662adfd5f1143c0be91e-eab131d1.jpg
